{"id":4134,"date":"2022-05-21T13:26:35","date_gmt":"2022-05-21T10:26:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/?p=4134"},"modified":"2022-05-21T13:26:35","modified_gmt":"2022-05-21T10:26:35","slug":"get-funky-in-the-sandbox-with-jamiroquai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/get-funky-in-the-sandbox-with-jamiroquai\/","title":{"rendered":"Get Funky in The Sandbox with Jamiroquai"},"content":{"rendered":"<p> <br \/>\n<\/p>\n<div itemprop=\"mainEntityOfPage\">\n<p>The good ol\u2019 funk and groove vibes are coming to the metaverse! The Sandbox has partnered up with <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/JamiroquaiHQ\">Jamiroquai<\/a>, the seminal jazz-funk band led by Jay Kay, to bring the group\u2019s free-spirited essence to virtual reality. Leading names in the music industry were involved in the fruition of the collaboration, including Bravado, Universal Music Group\u2019s industry-leading brand management division.<\/p>\n<p>For those who aren\u2019t acquainted with some of the finest music of the 90\u2019s, Jamiroquai is a legendary<strong> funk and acid jazz band<\/strong> from London. Known for the global smash, \u201cVirtual Insanity\u201d, and a string of hit albums and worldwide tours, the Grammy-winning band has sold more than 27 million albums worldwide. Its third album, <em>Travelling Without Moving<\/em>, received a Guinness World Record as the best-selling funk album in history.<\/p>\n<p>A special venue is being built in <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/TheSandboxGame\">The Sandbox<\/a> for Jamiroquai, where fans can come together in The Sandbox for a bit of funk, freedom, and fashion and connect with their favorite band in a communal, digital space.<\/p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Gaming Expands in The Metaverse in 2022!\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/kQY4_avxx9o?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p>To celebrate the partnership, an exclusive <strong>Jamiroquai x Sandbox merchandise collection<\/strong> comprising a limited-edition t-shirt and keyring is available on <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/store.jamiroquai.com\/\">store.jamiroquai.com<\/a>. More details about the collaboration will be revealed in the coming months.<\/p>\n<p>\u201c<em>We are delighted to be able to help deliver a new element of interaction between our artists and their fans<\/em>,\u201d said Racheal Redfearn, SVP A&amp;R and Brand Management of Bravado. \u201c<em>The Sandbox allows artists to bring their music and creativity to the fan in a fully immersive experience. We are excited to be partnering with The Sandbox and can\u2019t wait to welcome you all into the world of Jamiroquai<\/em>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nftplazas\/\">Follow us on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n<p><small><em>*All investment\/financial opinions expressed by NFT Plazas are from the personal research and experience of our site moderators and are intended as educational material only. Individuals are required to fully research any product prior to making any kind of investment.<\/em><\/small><\/p>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtyp